title: RIP MY SHRED STICK: GALVESTON
description: The second Texas stop of our RMSS 2012 Summer Tour touched down at the Galveston Pier for some good ol' fashioned fun with 75 of Galveston's best young surfers. For the full report and pictures from the day at the beach with Rob Machado and Pat O'Connell, head over to hurley.com/rmss
